msgid ""
"When `local_path` is a directory and `remote_path` does not exist, "
"`remote_path` becomes the destination directory root."
msgstr ""
"`local_path` がディレクトリで `remote_path` が存在しない場合、 `remote_path` "
"が宛先ディレクトリのルートになります。"

